  "title": "Glorious Nutty Syrian Chicken Pilaf",
  "description": "A nutty and creamy Syrian dish featuring chicken stock cube, this recipe is a gluten-free friendly option for a delicious meal, cooked to perfection on a slate-tile vessel.",
